citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:01pm on January
3, 2024.
Upon arrival to the facility, the inspector attempted to contact the licensee and facility representative via the phone
numbers on file, leaving a voicemail message for the facility representative. The licensee’s voicemail mailbox was full.
The inspector waited 30 minutes before leaving the facility.
End Section
